3030
01:38:35,410 --> 01:38:36,480
Pull yourself together!

3031
01:38:37,980 --> 01:38:39,080
Here I go.

3032
01:38:39,250 --> 01:38:41,390
- Go! - Ji Hyo!

3033
01:38:41,390 --> 01:38:44,220
- Ji Hyo! - Can you believe this?
